  <datafield tag="246" ind1=" " ind2=" ">
    <subfield code="9">arXiv</subfield>
    <subfield code="a">The gravitational two-body problem in the vicinity of the light ring: Insights from the black-hole-ring toy model</subfield>
  </datafield>
